the name of the game is break-through.
load init-breakthrough.
ok.
you can move your piece onto a location that is movable by the piece.
if a block is red then it is your.
if an object is a block then it is a piece.
if a location below your piece is under a location and the location is clear then it is movable by the piece.
if a location is not below an object then it is clear.
load second-breakthrough.
if an occupied location is attackable by a your piece then you can move a piece on the occupied location onto a garbage and move your piece onto the occupied location.
a location that is below a blue piece is occupied.
if a location is above an object that is below a piece and the location is diagonal with the object then the location is attackable by the piece.
load final-breakthrough.
the goal is that a red location is captured.
a location that is below your piece is captured.
ok.
load fail-breakthrough.
if a blue location is occupied then you lose.
ok.
done.
